videos.description: Jeremy Harris collects the steal and hits a streaking Dontay Caruthers, who glides in for a right-handed Buffalo dunk.
videos.headline: Buffalo's Caruthers crushes tomahawk slam

videos.description: Jayvon Graves is rewarded for his active hands on the other end for a fast-break dunk, ballooning the Bulls' lead to 30.
videos.headline: Buffalo's Graves ices the cake with breakaway slam
